full_threads.body:
Hi Heath


Can I ask you to make the amendment below please to https://www.msaustralia.org.au/about-us/our-people/our-team/ as I do not have capacity at the moment. Thank you. Can you let me know when this is completed.


Can you please help us with this update on your website?
  1. As Tara has gone on maternity leave, can you withhold, until her return, showing her bio?
  2. Add my bio (Laura Henschke) to the team.
I enclose a copy and photo you might want to consider using.


Also, I have forwarded the invoice for $9000 to MSA Accounts today.


Thank you.


Regards



Sarah
